En las tiendas generales se pueden comprar diversos artículos destinados al turismo, que también son útiles si se planea llevar a cabo una guerra de guerrillas, como brújulas, relojes o prismáticos. Las tiendas de ropa pueden ser útiles si quieres deshacerte de tu uniforme y mezclarte entre la multitud. Si tiene intención de que le disparen, asegúrese de visitar la farmacia de antemano.

Source: Problems were detected with one or more of selected factions. Please report this problem to the integration author along with complete log files.
An unknown error occured. Check logs for details and report this to the mod authors.
Scenario or terrain validation failed. Please report this problem to the scenario author along with a full set of log files.

Please keep in mind this project is in an early access state. Some features may not be fully developed yet, or may be temporary or placeholders.

Be sure to check out your journal and the Field Manual so you don't get lost.

If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to join our Discord community by scanning the code.

Good luck!
Translation:
Ten en cuenta que este proyecto se encuentra en un estado de acceso anticipado. Algunas características pueden no estar completamente desarrolladas aún, o pueden ser temporales o marcadores de posición.

Asegúrate de revisar tu diario y el Manual de Campo para no perderte.

Si tienes alguna pregunta o comentario, no dudes en unirte a nuestra comunidad de Discord escaneando el código.

¡Buena suerte!

Source: Start an uprising and lead your people to freedom in this open-world persistent campaign.
Translation: Inicia un levantamiento y conduce a tu gente hacia la libertad en esta campaña persistente de mundo abierto.
Multiplicador de producción de la fábrica
Multiplicador de coste de recuperación por distancia
Multiplicador de coste de retirada del garaje
Margen de beneficio de la tienda

Source: Base amount received by players periodically from each supporter of the resistance.
Translation: Cantidad base recibida periodicamente por el jugador de cada partidario de la resistencia.
Tiempo para que pase la busqueda y captura

Source: Players will become wanted if they are seen in clothes bloodied above this level. Set to 0 to disable.
Enables an epinephrine injector item, which instantly recovers full health. Disabling this option on existing saves will not remove items from the world, but they will not be usable.
Dynamically adjusts loot found on killed enemies, making scavenging for items more diverse and sustained use of enemy weapons more challenging. Disable if you want abundance of enemy equipment.
Can the epinephrine be self-administered by a downed player.
How long does the player have to withstand in the downed state in order to self-administer epinephrine.
How long does it take to lose maximum heat level (wanted state).
Translation: Cuanto se tarda en perder el nivel de busqueda maximo

Source: Automatically resupplies AI units with ammunition and consumable items as they are used. Enable for longer and more intense firefights, disable if you use other mods that enable AI to resupply autonomously.
Only relevant in multiplayer. If turned off, any already locked player containers will become accessible, but the ownership data is not cleared, and the setting may be reverted.
Only relevant in multiplayer. If turned off, any already locked vehicles will become accessible, but the ownership data is not cleared, and the setting may be reverted.
Enable to treat players who are missing shirts, pants or shoes as combatants.

Translation: Tiempo para que pase la búsqueda y captura en vehículo
Indicador de nivel de busqueda del personaje
Indicador de nivel de busqueda del vehiculo
Iconos de estado con las etiquetas con nombres

Source: Displays status indicators of other players in their nametags. Specific indicators have to be also enabled in HUD section.
Translation: Mostrar indicadores de estado de otros jugadores en sus nombres. Indicadores especificos tienen que estar habilitados tambien en  la sección del HUD.

Source: Options other than Default require third person view to be enabled in Reforger server settings.
Translation: Las opciones que no sean <b>Por defecto</> necesitan que la tercera persona esté habilitada en el servidor Reforger.

Source: Respawn money cost is not deducted if player's balance is below this threshold.
Should this item be always included in player inventory when spawning as a resistance fighter.
Cost of respawning as a resistance member in operating bases.
Number of supporters deducted for spawning as a civilian.
Higher stock levels allow faster early-game progression, since you can start raiding factories earlier. This only affects the initial allocation.
Translation: Stocks más altos permiten un progreso inicial más rápido, ya que puedes asaltar fábricas más pronto. Esto solo afecta a las cantidades iniciales.

Source: Resistance supporters act as respawn tickets. Increase this if you're playing in a larger group.
Translation: Los partidarios de la resistencia actuan como tickets de reaparición. Aumenta esto si jugais con un grupo grande.

Source: Clustered distribution will place your initial supporters in the same region of the map. Spreaded will randomize them throughout entire map, which can make the beginning harder on large maps.
Translation: Un apoyo agrupado colocará a tus partidarios en la misma región del mapa. Un apoyo desperdigado los colocará aleatoriamente por todo el mapa, que hará más dificil el comienzo el mapas más grandes.harder on large maps.

Source: This amount is given to each new player on their first spawn.
Translation: Esta cantidad se le dá a cada nuevo jugador al aparecer por primera vez.

Source: This hideout is not operational due to imminent danger.
Translation: Este escondite no está operativo debido a un peligro inminente.
Aquí no se puede construir nada.

Source: You cannot do that with a disabled radio.
Translation: No se puede hacer eso con una radio desactivada.

Source: You cannot do this with enemies nearby.
Translation: No puedes hacerlo con enemigos cerca.

Source: You cannot do this in illegal zone.
Translation: No puedes hacerlo en zona ilegal.

Source: Your vehicle must not be moving to do this.
Translation: Tu vehículo no debe estar en movimiento para hacer esto.

Source: You cannot do that while in vehicle.
Translation: No puedes hacerlo mientras está en el vehículo.

Source: You do not have enough money.
You do not have required resources.
Translation: No dispones de los recursos necesarios.

Source: You cannot do that while undercover.
Translation: No puedes hacer eso mientras estás de incógnito.

Source: You cannot do that while carrying weapons or in uniform. Hide your weapon and/or swap clothes.
Translation: No puedes hacerlo portando armas o de uniforme. Esconde tu arma y/o cámbiate de ropa.

Source: You cannot do that while being wanted. Wait until heat drops off and come back later.
Translation: No puedes hacerlo mientras te buscan. Espera a que dejen de buscarte y vuelve más tarde.

Source: You need a map to do that.
Translation: Para eso se necesita un mapa.

Source: You need a watch to do that.
Translation: Para eso se necesita un reloj.

Source: You extorted change money from this person. They will support the enemy from now on!
Translation: Has extorsionado dinero de esta persona. ¡A partir de ahora apoyarán al enemigo!

Source: This person has no money to extort.
Translation: Esta persona no tiene dinero que extorsionar.

Source: This person already supports the resistance.
Translation: Esta persona ya apoya a la resistencia.

Source: You have convinced this person to support resistance.
Translation: Has convencido a esta persona para que apoye a la resistencia.

Source: This person supports enemy and cannot be convinced to your cause.
Translation: Esta persona apoya al enemigo y no puede ser convencida para que nos apoye.

Source: You failed to convince this person to support your cause.
Translation: No has conseguido convencer a esta persona para que apoye tu causa.

Source: You can't talk with this person right now.
Translation: No puedes hablar con esta persona ahora mismo.

Source: There are no destinations you can fast travel to right now.
Translation: Ahora mismo no hay destinos a los que puedas viajar rápidamente.

Source: Destination is too close to fast travel.
Translation: El destino está demasiado cerca para viaje rápido.

Source: This vehicle cannot be parked on this type of spot.
Translation: Este vehículo no puede estacionarse en este tipo de plaza.

Source: Vehicle has been parked. You can now use the garage to retrieve the vehicle from far away.
Translation: El vehículo ha sido aparcado. Ahora puedes utilizar el garaje para recuperar el vehículo desde lejos.

Source: This vehicle is too large to fit into that parking spot.
Translation: Este vehículo es demasiado grande para caber en esa plaza de aparcamiento.
No se pudo adquirir el vehiculo.

Source: Vehicle cannot be retrieved because the parking spot is obstructed.
Translation: No se puede recuperar el vehículo porque la plaza de aparcamiento está obstruida.

Source: Vehicle is too close to be retrieved.
Translation: El vehículo está demasiado cerca para ser recuperado.

Source: Another vehicle is already assigned to this parking slot. You can abandon that vehicle and free up the spot by accessing garage management.
Translation: Ya hay otro vehículo asignado a esta plaza de aparcamiento. Puedes abandonar ese vehículo y liberar la plaza accediendo a la gestión del garaje.

Source: There is no vehicle assigned to the parking spot.
Translation: No hay ningún vehículo asignado a la plaza de aparcamiento.

Source: You do not have enough space in inventory to store the item. It has been placed on the ground.
You failed to pick the lock.
There is no one nearby to transfer money to.
Translation: No hay nadie cerca a quien transferir dinero.

Source: You are too far away to transfer money.
Translation: Estás demasiado lejos para transferir dinero.

Source: The same faction cannot be used as civilians and a conflict side simultaneously. Please select different factions to continue.
Translation: No se puede usar la misma facción como civil y como bando en conflicto simultáneamente. Selecciona facciones diferentes para continuar.

Source: The same faction cannot be used as enemy and allied forces simultaneously. Please select different factions to continue.
Translation: No se puede usar la misma facción como fuerzas enemigas y aliadas simultáneamente. Por favor, selecciona facciones diferentes para continuar.

Source: The same faction cannot be selected for players and another conflict side simultaneously. Please select different factions to continue.
Translation: No se puede seleccionar la misma facción para los jugadores y otro bando en conflicto simultáneamente. Por favor, selecciona facciones diferentes para continuar.

Source: You have abandoned ownership over this item.
Translation: Has abandonado la titularidad de este objeto.

Source: You claimed ownership over this item. This allows you to control who can access it.
Translation: Has tomado posesión de este elemento. Esto te permite controlar quién puede acceder a él.

Source: This item cannot be attached to this object.
Translation: Este elemento no puede pegarse a este objeto.
Aquí no se puede colocar nada.

Source: You are too close to an enemy checkpoint to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de un punto de control enemigo para colocarlo aquí.

Source: You are too close to an enemy camp to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de un campamento enemigo para colocarlo aquí.

Source: You are too close to a factory to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de una fábrica para colocarla aquí.

Source: You cannot place this in an illegal zone.
Translation: No se puede colocar en una zona ilegal.

Source: You are too close to a military base to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de una base militar para colocarla aquí.

Source: You are too close to a camp to place here.
You are too close to an existing FOB to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de un FOB existente para colocarlo aquí.

Source: You are too close to a port to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de un puerto para colocarlo aquí.

Source: You are too close to an enemy radar site to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de un radar enemigo para colocarlo aquí.

Source: You are too close to an enemy radio tower to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de una torre de radio enemiga para colocarla aquí.

Source: You are too close to a town to place here.
Translation: Estás demasiado cerca de una ciudad para colocarla aquí.

Source: No more objects can be placed in this area.
This item has to be placed on a vertical surface.
Translation: Este objeto debe colocarse sobre una superficie vertical.

Source: A poster has been already placed here.
Translation: Ya se ha colocado un cartel aquí.

Source: Selected placement is too close to another poster.
Translation: La ubicación seleccionada está demasiado cerca de otro cartel.

Source: No more posters can be placed in this area.
Translation: No se pueden colocar más carteles en esta zona.

Source: There is no space left to store the resources.
Translation: No queda espacio para almacenar los recursos.

Source: This respawn location is now unavailable.
Translation: Este punto de respawn ya no está disponible.

Source: You can't respawn at any location right now.
Translation: Ahora mismo no puedes reaparecer en ningún sitio.

Source: This shop is currently closed. Come back later within business hours.
Translation: Esta tienda está actualmente cerrada. Vuelva más tarde dentro del horario comercial.

Source: You have no space in your inventory to buy this item.
Translation: No tienes espacio en tu inventario para comprar este artículo.

Source: Not enough space in storage to perform purchase.
Translation: No hay espacio suficiente en el almacén para realizar la compra.

Source: You do not have any supplies that could be donated.
Translation: No llevas suministros que puedan donarse.

Source: You have donated supplies to the town.
Translation: Has donado suministros a la ciudad.

Source: %1, a civilian, has been killed near %2.
Translation: %1, un civil, ha sido asesinado cerca de %2.

Source: %1 has been killed by friendly fire near %2.
Translation: %1 ha muerto por fuego amigo cerca de %2.

Source: %1, a %3 fighter, has been killed near %2.
Translation: %1, un combatiente %3, ha sido asesinado cerca de %2.

Source: %1, a %3 fighter, has been killed near %2 by friendly fire.
Translation: %1, un combatiente %3, ha muerto cerca de %2 por fuego amigo.

Source: Medium size civilian backpack produced on Nogova. Copy of a US design.
Locked briefcase with unknown, but seemingly very important contents.
Can be used to establish a camp, creating a jump-off point for the resistance. After placing, the camp can be dismantled and the kit may be reused.
Largest backpack from the Batohárna Lipany product line, copy of a US design.
Small tourist backpack, copy of a Soviet design.
Tents can be deployed at camps to enable respawning. They are single use, but can be picked up and moved.
Small personal backpack, a copy of Soviet military design. Produced by Batohárna Lipany n.p. on Nogova.
Soaked in blood. Wearing this will make you suspicious.
%1 uses passphrases to avoid deconspiration, as listed in the schedule below. Make sure to use the correct one when contacting resistance members to authenticate yourself.
Translation: %1 utiliza contraseñas para evitar la detección, tal y como se indica en la lista de abajo. Asegúrate de utilizar la correcta cuando te pongas en contacto con miembros de la resistencia para autenticarte.

Source: %1 changes its operating radio frequency according to the listing below. To establish radio communication with HQ, you must use the correct passphrase while within range of a controlled radio tower.
Translation: %1 cambia su frecuencia de radio operativa de acuerdo con el siguiente listado. Para establecer comunicación por radio con el Cuartel General, debe utilizar la contraseña correcta mientras se encuentra dentro del alcance de una torre de radio controlada.

Source: The occupier has deployed a SOF group to hunt one of our leaders down. Luckily enough, we have intel on their camping location. Find the camp and eliminate the group.
You have to deliver a very important... whatever. It's not your business. The briefcase is locked anyway. Just don't lose it and bring it in one piece to the recipient.

We need distraction. Engage with the enemy garrison and stay in contact until they launch an alarm. Do not try to capture it, once the alarm goes off you should back off immediately. This will be enough to keep their QRF busy for a moment.
Our intelligence has credible information that captives are currently being held at one of the enemy prisons.
Ensure that none of the captives are killed during the escape, as this would put us in a very bad light.
Your task is to liberate them and escort them to a safe location, out of enemy fire and at a reasonable distance from the prison.
We received information about a high value target being present at one of the enemy locations. Your task is to eliminate the target by any means necessary. Once done, report back to the resistance.
Simple tool that can be used to open locks.
Translation: Herramienta simple que se puede usar para fozar cerraduras.

Source: Produces %1 supplies per hour between 8:00 and 16:00 when under control of the resistance.
Translation: Produce %1 suministros por hora entre las 8:00 y las 16:00 cuando está bajo el control de la resistencia.

Source: Keep control by maintaining at least %1% population support.
Translation: Retén el control manteniendo al menos un %1% de apoyo de la población.

Source: Destroy all radars to neutralize the site.
Translation: Destruye todos los radares para neutralizar el sitio.

Source: Take control by raising population support to %1% and keeping the threat level below %2%.
Translation: Toma el control aumentando el apoyo de la población a %1% y manteniendo el nivel de amenaza por debajo de %2%.

Source: Start the battle by increasing the threat level to %2% and ensuring at least %1% population support.
Translation: Comienza la batalla aumentando el nivel de amenaza a %2% y asegurando al menos %1% de apoyo de la población.

Source: Establish a hideout by raising population support to %1%.
Translation: Establece un escondite aumentando el apoyo de la población al %1%.

Source: Keep population support above %1% to maintain the hideout.
Translation: Mantén el apoyo de la población por encima del %1% para mantener el escondite.
La resistencia tomó el control de %1.

Source: The resistance failed to take control over %1.
Translation: La resistencia no pudo tomar el control de %1.
La resistencia tomó el control de %1.

Source: The resistance failed to take control over %1.
Translation: La resistencia no pudo tomar el control de %1.

Source: Military radar site near %1 has been destroyed by the resistance.
Translation: El radar militar cerca de %1 ha sido destruido por la resistencia.

Source: The resistance has captured a radio tower near %1.
Translation: La resistencia ha capturado una torre de radio cerca de %1.

Source: The resistance defended their control over %1.
Translation: La resistencia defendió su control sobre %1.

Source: The resistance failed to take control over %1.
Translation: La resistencia no pudo tomar el control de %1.

Source: Delivery job failed, the contact person is dead.
Delivery job failed, destination hideout disbanded.
The resistance cleared an enemy camp near %1.
Translation: La resistencia despejó un campamento enemigo cerca de %1.

Source: The uprising started by %1 has been crushed. %2 remains under %3 control.
Translation: El levantamiento iniciado por %1 ha sido aplastado. %2 permanece bajo el control de %3.

Source: %1 has won the uprising and took control over %2. Good job!
Translation: %1 ha ganado el levantamiento y ha tomado el control de %2. ¡Buen trabajo!

Source: A new revolution has started. Rise up, people of %1!
Translation: Ha comenzado una nueva revolución. ¡Arriba, gente de %1!

Source: The resistance hideout in %1 is back in operation.
Translation: El escondite de la resistencia en %1 vuelve a estar operativo.

Source: The resistance hideout in %1 has been shut down.
Translation: El escondite de la resistencia en %1 ha sido cerrado.

Source: The resistance has established a new hideout in %1.
Translation: La resistencia ha establecido un nuevo escondite en %1.

Source: The resistance HQ near %1 has been shut down due to imminent danger.
Translation: El cuartel general de la resistencia cerca de %1 ha sido desactivado debido a un peligro inminente.

Source: The resistance has established a new HQ hideout.
Translation: La resistencia ha establecido un nuevo escondite HQ.

Source: The %1 HQ near %2 is shut down due to operator death.
Translation: El cuartel general %1 cerca de %2 está apagado debido a la muerte del operador.

Source: The resistance hideout in %1 is inoperable due to imminent danger.
Translation: El escondite de la resistencia en %1 está inoperativo debido a un peligro inminente.

Source: The %1 hideout in %2 is shut down due to operator death.
Translation: El escondite %1 en %2 está cerrado debido a la muerte del operador.

Source: The resistance failed to free any prisoners in a jailbreak attempt.
%1 has been destroyed by enemy forces.

Translation: %2 ha sido establecido por %1 cerca de %3.

Source: You receive %1 for completing the job.
Radio tower near %1 has been destroyed.
Translation: Torre de radio cerca de %1 ha sido destruida.
Guarda tus objetos de forma segura.

Source: Inventory storage box with reasonable capacity for personal equipment. Can be locked to protect the items.
Translation: Caja de almacenamiento de inventario con capacidad razonable para equipamiento personal. Puede cerrarse con llave para proteger los artículos.

Source: Placing the flag will establish a new operating base.
Translation: Al colocar la bandera se establecerá una nueva base de operaciones.

Source: The light can be switched on and off.
Translation: La luz puede encenderse y apagarse.

Source: Basic building block of a defensive position.
Translation: Componente básico de una posición defensiva.

Source: Please wait for the server administrator to configure and start a new game. If you are the administrator, please log in by typing the command below into the chat.
Translation: Por favor, espere a que el administrador del servidor configure e inicie una nueva partida. Si usted es el administrador, por favor inicie sesión escribiendo el comando de abajo en el chat.

Source: We encourage you to check out Field Manual to learn more about this game mode while you are waiting.
Translation: Te animamos a que consultes Manual de campo para saber más sobre este modo de juego mientras esperas.

Source: Posters can be hanged in various places to increase civilian population support and increase visibility of the resistance.
Translation: Se pueden colgar carteles en diversos lugares para aumentar el apoyo de la población civil y aumentar la visibilidad de la resistencia.

Source: The radio tower has been destroyed and is inoperable.
Translation: La torre de radio ha sido destruida y no funciona.

Source: Spawning at this camp will consume 1 tent.
You will spawn as a resistance fighter.
Respawning at this location will take %1 supplies.
Translation: Reaparecer en este lugar requerirá %1 de suministros.

Source: Click on selected location to respawn.
Translation: Haz clic en la ubicación seleccionada para reaparecer.

Source: Click to respawn at this location.
Translation: Haz clic para reaparecer en este lugar.

Source: Respawn will reduce population support by %1.
Translation: Respawn reducirá el apoyo a la población en 1.

Source: You will spawn in civilian clothes, with a handgun and a map.
Translation: Aparecerás vestido de civil, con una pistola y un mapa.

Source: This respawn location is not available due to ongoing battle.
Translation: Este lugar de reaparición no está disponible debido a una batalla en curso.

Source: Cannot respawn while enemies are present at this location.
Translation: No puedes reaparecer mientras haya enemigos en este lugar.

Source: This respawn location is not available at the moment.
Translation: Este lugar de reaparición no está disponible en este momento.

Source: You need local population support to respawn at this location.
Translation: Necesitas el apoyo de la población local para reaparecer en este lugar.

Source: No tents are available at this camp for respawn.
Spawning here requires at least %1 supplies in storage.
Translation: Reaparecer aquí requiere al menos %1 de suministros almacenados.

Source: This location must be under resistance control to respawn.
Translation: Esta ubicación debe estar bajo control de la resistencia para reaparecer.

Source: There are no items in your inventory to sell.
Translation: No hay artículos en tu inventario para vender.

Source: There are no items available for purchase.
Translation: No hay artículos disponibles para la compra.

Source: You are a bunch of terrorists. You should be arrested.
Translation: Sois una panda de terroristas. Deberíais ser arrestados.

Source: The regime brought order, and you people just want chaos.
Translation: El régimen trajo el orden, y vosotros sólo queréis el caos.

Source: I hope they find you. I'll be the one pointing the gun.
Translation: Espero que te encuentren. Yo seré el que apunte el arma.

Source: I stand with the ones who actually protect this place, not you.
Translation: Yo estoy con los que realmente protegen este lugar, no tú.

Source: I'll make sure authorities learn about it.
Translation: Me aseguraré de que las autoridades se enteren.

Source: That just sounds like another way to die.
Translation: Eso suena como otra forma de morir.

Source: Change? That's a fairy tale. I'm just trying to stay alive.
Translation: ¿Cambio? Eso es un cuento de hadas. Sólo intento seguir vivo.

Source: Get lost. I don't need your cause or your problems.
Translation: Piérdete. No necesito tu causa ni tus problemas.

Source: I'm not cut out for that kind of thing. Sorry.
Translation: No estoy hecho para ese tipo de cosas. Lo siento.

Source: I tried once. It didn't end well.
Translation: Lo intenté una vez. No terminó bien.
¿Unirme a ti? No soy un suicida.

Source: Already embedded. I just don't advertise it.
Translation: Ya os apoyo. Sólo que no lo anuncio.

Source: You're not the first to ask. I signed up a while ago.
Translation: No eres el primero que me pregunta. Me apunté hace tiempo.

Source: You guys seriously need to talk to each other. I'm with you.
Translation: En serio, tenéis que hablar entre vosotros. Ya os apoyo.

Source: You don't need to convince me. I've bled for this already.
Translation: No necesitas convencerme. Ya he sangrado por la causa.

Source: Count me in. It's time someone stood up to them.
Translation: Cuenta conmigo. Es hora de que alguien les haga frente.
Ya me he cansado de mirar. Peleemos.

Source: Tell your people I'm ready. Let's get to work.
Translation: Dile a tu gente que estoy listo. Manos a la obra.

Source: I'm in. Just tell me what needs to be done.
Translation: Me apunto. Sólo dime lo que hay que hacer.

Source: Hell yeah. Let's mess them up.
Translation: Claro que sí. Vamos a liarla.

Source: That supposed to scare me? Try harder.
Translation: ¿Se supone que eso debe asustarme? Esfuérzate más.

Source: I've got nothing for you, except regret.
Translation: No tengo nada para ti, excepto arrepentimiento.

Source: Get lost, I'm not scared of you.
Translation: Anda por ahí, no te tengo miedo.

Source: You're not the first to try.
Translation: No eres el primero que lo intenta.

Source: Alright, alright! Just don't hurt me!
Translation: ¡Está bien, está bien! ¡No me hagas daño!

Source: It was for my kid's medicine... but whatever. Take it.
Translation: Era para la medicina de mi hijo... pero da igual. Tómalo.
No eres más que un matón.

Source: You are worse than the regime.
Fine, but you just lost a supporter.
Translation: Bien, pero acabas de perder un partidario.

Source: I'm sure the resistance will pay back for this.
Translation: Estoy seguro de que la resistencia pagará por esto.

Source: You are just bandits in uniforms.
Translation: No sois más que ladrones con uniforme.

Source: Wear some pants before you talk to me.
I'm not talking to naked strangers.
I have nothing to say to you.
Do you have something for me?
You look like someone who's had enough. Join us.
Translation: Tienes cara de que ya has tenido suficiente. Únete a nosotros.

Source: I have enough of these pigs. Are you in, or are you just surviving?
Translation: Estoy harto de estos cerdos. ¿Te apuntas o sólo sobrevives?

Source: If you're tired of hiding, pick up a cause worth dying for.
Translation: Si estás cansado de esconderte, elige una causa por la que merezca la pena morir.

Source: Not everyone's blind to what's going on. Some of us are doing something about it.
Translation: No todos estamos ciegos ante lo que ocurre. Algunos estamos haciendo algo al respecto.

Source: Are you willing to make a difference? Because we are.
Translation: ¿Está dispuesto a marcar la diferencia? Porque nosotros sí.

Source: We've got fire, we've got purpose - all we're missing is you.
Translation: Tenemos ímpetu, tenemos un propósito, lo único que nos falta eres tú.

Source: You want change? You don't get it by sitting around. Join us.
Translation: ¿Quieres cambiar? No lo conseguirás quedándote de brazos cruzados. Únete a nosotros.

Source: You sick of their boot on your neck? Then maybe it's time to push back.
Translation: ¿Estás harto de que te maltraten? Entonces tal vez sea hora de contraatacar.

Source: Orders? We make our own now. Join us.
Translation: ¿Órdenes? Ahora las damos nosotros. Únete a nosotros.

Source: There's a war coming whether you're ready or not. Best be on the right side.
Translation: Se avecina una guerra, estés preparado o no. Mejor estar en el bando correcto.

Source: I'm not asking twice. Money, now.
Translation: No voy a pedirlo dos veces. Dinero, ahora.

Source: You pay now, or you bleed later. Simple math.
Translation: O pagas ahora o sangras después. Simple matemática.

Source: Protection doesn't come free. Give me your money.
Translation: La protección no es gratis. Dame tu dinero.

Source: This is the part where you give me what I want.
Translation: Esta es la parte en la que me das lo que quiero.

Source: Last guy who said no is still chewing through a straw.
Translation: El último que dijo que no, sigue necesitando una pajita para comer.

Source: I'm ready to do whatever it takes to help our cause.
Translation: Estoy dispuesto a hacer lo que haga falta para ayudar a nuestra causa.

Source: Hey, we talked earlier. I want to join the fight.
Translation: Oye, hablamos antes. Quiero unirme a la lucha.

Source: I have to pass this one to someone else.
This is not a job for me.
Get out of here, you are free.
I am getting you out of here.
Got any more of those posters?
There are people with guns, we're scared, can you send a patrol over here?
Translation: Hay gente armada, tenemos miedo, ¿puede enviar una patrulla?

Source: More enemies are eating dirt. Here's proof.
Translation: Más enemigos han caído. Aquí está la prueba.

Source: So, you want to take it to the next level?
We are running an... um... incentive scheme of sorts.
Translation: Estamos llevando a cabo una especie de plan de incentivos.

Source: Certain friends of our cause are offering money for every eliminated enemy soldier.
Translation: Ciertos amigos de nuestra causa ofrecen dinero por cada soldado enemigo eliminado.

Source: They don't buy our word, but enemy dogtags are solid proof.
Translation: No se tragan nuestra palabra, pero las placas enemigas son una prueba sólida.

Source: Bring me a handful of those if you're not joking around.
Translation: Tráeme un puñado de esas si no estás bromeando.

Source: Your next task is to set up a field operating base.
Translation: Su siguiente tarea es establecer una base de operaciones.

Source: Pick a good spot for it. You can use your map to check which areas are too dangerous.
Translation: Elige un buen lugar para ello. Puedes usar tu mapa para comprobar qué zonas son demasiado peligrosas.

Source: You'll need some money to kick it off. Oh, and don't forget a shovel.
Translation: Necesitarás dinero para empezar. Ah, y no olvides una pala.

Source: Make sure you are not followed.
Translation: Asegúrese de que no le siguen.

Source: Very well then. But we need more people before we take up arms. Actually, there is something you can do for us.
Translation: Muy bien. Pero necesitamos más gente antes de tomar las armas. En realidad, hay algo que puedes hacer por nosotros.

Source: Take this briefcase. I need you to deliver it to someone. Don't look inside.
You're calling just in time. Grab instructions from the dead drop at coordinates:
Translation: Llamas justo a tiempo. Toma las instrucciones del punto de entrega en las coordenadas:

Source: Yes. Come visit me for further instructions.
Translation: Sí. Ven a visitarme para más instrucciones.

Source: I'm glad you came. Take this note with instructions.
Translation: Me alegro de que hayas venido. Toma esta nota con instrucciones.

Source: Well done. I wish we had more like you in our ranks.
Translation: Bien hecho. Ojalá tuviéramos más como tú en nuestras filas.

Source: Report back to me in person after the job is done.
Translation: Infórmame en persona una vez hayas acabado el trabajo.

Source: Shame, I thought you were capable.
Think twice before you waste my time again.
I am not around. Reach me out when things get calmer.
Translation: No estoy disponible. Llámame cuando las cosas se calmen.

Source: Not right now, but check back later.
Translation: Ahora no, pero prueba más tarde.

Source: We have to spread the word. Visit nearby towns and hang a bunch of revolutionary posters.
Translation: Tenemos que correr la voz. Visita los pueblos cercanos y cuelga un montón de carteles revolucionarios.

Source: Look for cabinets, advertisement boards, signs and other things that attract attention.
Translation: Busca armarios, paneles publicitarios, señales y otras cosas que llamen la atención.

Source: This is illegal, make sure you are not seen putting these up, or at least don't get yourself killed.
Translation: Esto es ilegal, asegúrate de que no te vean colocándolas, o al menos que no te maten.

Source: You already have enough posters with you. It's too dangerous to carry more.
Translation: Ya llevas suficientes carteles contigo. Es demasiado peligroso llevar más.

Source: I don't have any more left at the moment.
Translation: No me quedan más por el momento.

Source: Make some space in your bag if you want the posters.
Translation: Haz sitio en tu bolsa si quieres los carteles.
Buen trabajo, aquí tienes tu recompensa.

Source: I was expecting you. Thanks for the delivery.
You've reached the Military Police post. How can I help you?
Translation: Ha llamdo al puesto de la Policía Militar. ¿En qué puedo ayudarle?

Source: Hang tight, we will dispatch someone your way immediately.
Translation: Espere ahí, enviaremos a alguien de inmediato.

Source: This vehicle type cannot be repaired at this support station.
Translation: Este tipo de vehículo no puede repararse en esta estación de apoyo.

Source: Curfew is in effect from %1 to %2.
Translation: El toque de queda está en vigor de %1 a %2.
La ley marcial está en vigor.
